lead_paragraph: Cristiano Ronaldo scored one goal and inadvertently set up the other as Portugal ground out a 2-0 win over Wales on Wednesday to march into the Euro 2016 final.

headline.print_headline: Ronaldo Delivers as Portugal End Dream Wales Run
